            <lg xml:id="TK151">
<l>akaḻvārait tāṅku nilampōlat tammai </l>
<l>yikaḻvārp poṟutta ṟalai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To bear with one's detractors, just as the Earth bears up</l>
<l>those who dig into it, is the main thing.</l>
